thrown in the slammer again.

05:57.358 --> 05:58.557
You're crazy.

05:58.559 --> 06:00.592
Come here,
you little piece of shit.

06:00.594 --> 06:01.960
Come here! Come here!

06:01.962 --> 06:04.363
Man!

06:04.365 --> 06:05.897
Yes!

06:05.899 --> 06:08.667
Oh, there's only one thing
worse than little punks.

06:08.669 --> 06:09.835
What's that?

