Is a pretty little thing.

06:28.821 --> 06:30.889
Yeah, she's really pretty.

06:30.891 --> 06:32.090
Mm-hmm.

06:40.800 --> 06:42.968
It's, um, 25 cents, hon.

06:46.606 --> 06:47.939
You can keep it.

06:49.442 --> 06:51.410
Uh, thank--thank you.

06:51.412 --> 06:52.677
Bye.

06:52.679 --> 06:53.812
Bye.

06:55.615 --> 06:58.550
Hey, it's okay
to have a crush on her.

06:58.552 --> 06:59.751
Oh, Peg! Come on.

06:59.753 --> 07:01.653
No. Hey, I can tell, angel.

07:05.592 --> 07:06.825
Hey, Vicki!

07:06.827 --> 07:10.061
So the theme could be
anything you like.

07:10.063 --> 07:13.799
Well, let's remember to keep some
clothes on our subjects, okay?

07:15.502 --> 07:17.068
- Ryan.
- But, Mr. Sullivan,

07:17.070 --> 07:19.838
what if they want
to take their clothes off?

07:21.208 --> 07:23.608
Now if anyone wants
to enter the contest,

07:23.610 --> 07:27.646
here. Pick up one of these
applications as you leave.

07:37.657 --> 07:40.125
Just let me know. Just--No...

07:51.571 --> 07:53.872
I had the bat, and I was like--

07:53.874 --> 07:56.708
I was like, "Leave her alone."

07:56.710 --> 07:59.811
It was--
It was insane.

07:59.813 --> 08:02.247
Wh-What was her name again?

08:02.249 --> 08:04.049
- Vicki.
- Vicki?

08:04.051 --> 08:05.784
Yeah. She kind of like--

08:05.786 --> 08:09.254
Truck stop's like her--
Like her hangout...

08:09.256 --> 08:10.522
Hmm. or...

08:12.258 --> 08:15.794
You know, when I went out there,
I felt like a regular guy,

08:15.796 --> 08:19.931
