have done what you did.

08:27.274 --> 08:29.007
I'm proud of you.

08:34.580 --> 08:37.115
Well, it did feel pretty good.

08:39.852 --> 08:43.121
When I went back inside,
I felt like an alien again.

08:53.734 --> 08:55.834
Hey, Charles, uh,

08:55.836 --> 08:57.569
we are gonna have
to start talk--

08:57.571 --> 08:58.803
