only a couple years old,

23:40.653 --> 23:41.719
just started to walk.

23:41.721 --> 23:43.120
At least, tried to walk.

23:43.122 --> 23:44.989
Why'd she leave?

23:46.091 --> 23:48.058
Me.

23:49.928 --> 23:52.463
So it's just you
and your dad now?

23:52.465 --> 23:54.465
Yeah, my dad's great.

23:54.467 --> 23:55.833
He's like my best friend.

23:55.835 --> 23:58.702
