take the picture.

24:29.035 --> 24:31.001
We kind of have to go, right?

24:31.003 --> 24:33.003
Yeah.

24:56.194 --> 24:59.263
No, no, no! I am done
with men, remember?

24:59.265 --> 25:01.765
D-O-N-E, done.

25:01.767 --> 25:02.967
