25:25.791 --> 25:27.057
- Oh, oh...
- Listen to me, girls.

25:27.059 --> 25:28.526
I know from where I speak.

25:28.528 --> 25:29.927
Oh, honey, there are still

25:29.929 --> 25:31.662
some good men out there,
fine men out there.

25:31.664 --> 25:33.597
Still some good men.

25:33.599 --> 25:35.032
Well, I have met most
every man in this state,

25:35.034 --> 25:36.600
and I have yet
to find a good one.

25:36.602 --> 25:38.936
