25:38.938 --> 25:40.671
Oh, she's exaggerating.

25:40.673 --> 25:42.840
You guys didn't know me
when I was younger.

25:42.842 --> 25:44.882
The entire state is
not an exaggeration.

25:46.612 --> 25:48.812
You might be telling the truth.

25:48.814 --> 25:50.614
Oh, let's go.
I wanna--Let's move.

25:52.818 --> 25:54.752
- Hey, Dottie. Dottie.
- Yes, ma'am.

25:54.754 --> 25:55.953
Did you forget to wear
your underwear again?

25:55.955 --> 25:57.688
Well, of course I did.

26:00.325 --> 26:02.192
Yee-haw!

26:05.764 --> 26:07.731
You okay?

26:22.013 --> 26:23.280
Dad!

26:23.282 --> 26:25.015
Dad! You okay?

26:25.017 --> 26:26.684
Yeah. Yeah.

26:26.686 --> 26:27.718
I'm all right.

26:42.934 --> 26:44.268
You have fun?

26:45.837 --> 26:46.937
Yeah, I guess.

26:49.674 --> 26:51.141
Did you dance?

26:52.777 --> 26:54.745
You know I can't do that.

27:35.020 --> 27:36.253
Hey.

28:00.812 --> 28:02.713
Ah, there he is.

28:02.715 --> 28:03.881
Hey, Charles.

28:03.883 --> 28:05.449
Hey.

28:05.451 --> 28:06.450
Hi.

28:06.452 --> 28:07.951
Hey.

28:07.953 --> 28:10.254
