was just hanging out.

28:10.256 --> 28:12.856
Yeah, Vicki knows all
about cars and Harleys.

28:12.858 --> 28:14.992
Cool.

28:14.994 --> 28:18.462
I grew up being kind of a tomboy.
What can I say?

28:18.464 --> 28:20.764
And I love your dad's
Chevelle and Harley.

28:20.766 --> 28:21.865
They're the coolest.

28:25.371 --> 28:28.772
I figured we could go
to a lighthouse today.

28:48.861 --> 28:51.995
Can't believe how patient
you have to be to do this.

28:51.997 --> 28:53.430
That's what I love
about photography.

28:53.432 --> 28:56.266
Anything, really, if you
look at it long enough,

28:56.268 --> 28:58.802
