and this is Kate.

46:30.789 --> 46:32.355
Hi. Hi.

46:32.357 --> 46:34.056
Hi.

46:35.392 --> 46:38.961
So what are you doing out here?

46:38.963 --> 46:41.397
Um, I've been
helping Charles out

46:41.399 --> 46:42.899
with his photography project.

46:42.901 --> 46:45.935
We were just in the area.

46:45.937 --> 46:49.038
- Are you really a pr--
- Kate.

46:56.280 --> 46:58.047
So where are you living?

46:58.049 --> 46:59.382
Out in the desert.

46:59.384 --> 47:01.417
Are you coming home?

47:05.422 --> 47:07.590
How's school been?

47:07.592 --> 47:08.591
Fine.

47:08.593 --> 47:10.493
Yeah, it's okay.

47:12.162 --> 47:14.397
Well, it's--

47:14.399 --> 47:16.399
It's really good
to see you, Vicki.

47:18.268 --> 47:19.535
Do you mean that?

47:19.537 --> 47:22.038
Of course I mean that.

47:22.040 --> 47:23.339
Isn't it, girls?

47:23.341 --> 47:25.174
Yeah.

47:25.176 --> 47:27.143
Yeah.

47:52.035 --> 47:53.202
It's been--

47:53.204 --> 47:54.937
Well, let's see.

47:54.939 --> 47:57.039
We've known each other
for a few years now, right?

47:57.041 --> 47:58.074
Mm-hmm.

47:58.076 --> 47:59.475
