47:59.477 --> 48:02.144
my broken-down car into Sears.

48:02.146 --> 48:03.946
Good old Eric
fixed me up just fine.

48:05.550 --> 48:07.583
And then I met Charles,
and, well,

48:07.585 --> 48:09.218
he just completely
stole my heart.

48:09.220 --> 48:11.888
- Well, what about me?
- Eh, you wish.

48:13.491 --> 48:14.957
Nope, Charles is, has been,

48:14.959 --> 48:16.659
and always will be
the only man for me.

48:16.661 --> 48:19.095
Peg got me the job
at the truck stop.

48:19.097 --> 48:21.163
Oh, really? That's cool.

48:22.566 --> 48:26.636
Yep. Vicki, you know,
um, Charles showed me

48:26.638 --> 48:29.005
