that he took of you,

48:29.007 --> 48:31.173
and I'm telling you,
you could be a model.

48:31.175 --> 48:32.441
Me?

48:32.443 --> 48:34.043
Yeah.

48:34.045 --> 48:37.046
You, you are
the prettiest little thing.

48:37.048 --> 48:38.981
You do photograph very well.

48:38.983 --> 48:41.150
Your eyes are beautiful.

48:41.152 --> 48:42.385
