01:14:01.837 --> 01:14:04.939
Hey, Truck Stop.

01:14:04.941 --> 01:14:07.542
Hey, my man.

01:14:07.544 --> 01:14:09.210
Is that you?

01:14:09.212 --> 01:14:12.947
Oh, God damn it.

01:14:12.949 --> 01:14:15.716
God damn, is that who you
been running around with?

01:14:15.718 --> 01:14:16.984
No. No.

01:14:16.986 --> 01:14:19.454
A fucking cripple
from the truck stop?

01:14:19.456 --> 01:14:21.022
No.

01:14:21.024 --> 01:14:22.657
What?

01:14:22.659 --> 01:14:24.058
Charles, Charles,

01:14:24.060 --> 01:14:27.595
Charles, you have to go, please.

01:14:27.597 --> 01:14:30.998
What are you doing, Truck Stop?

01:14:31.000 --> 01:14:32.033
Huh?

01:14:32.035 --> 01:14:33.167
Leave her alone.

01:14:36.939 --> 01:14:40.041
I told you to stay
out of my business.

01:14:40.043 --> 01:14:42.043
I'm not fuckin'
playin' with you anymore.

01:14:42.045 --> 01:14:43.211
Charles! Whoa!

01:14:43.213 --> 01:14:46.714
You motherfucker.

01:14:46.716 --> 01:14:50.017
This is your last chance to
get the fuck outta here.

01:14:51.187 --> 01:14:53.921
Yeah.

01:14:53.923 --> 01:14:55.723
Oh, yeah.

01:14:55.725 --> 01:14:57.825
I can't let you
get away with that.

01:14:57.827 --> 01:14:59.494
No.

01:14:59.496 --> 01:15:00.862
What kind of a man would I be

01:15:00.864 --> 01:15:03.531
if I let you
get away with that, huh?

01:15:08.103 --> 01:15:10.238
Ah, man, I'll just
hit him again.

01:15:10.240 --> 01:15:11.639
No!

01:15:11.641 --> 01:15:13.074
Back away from me!

01:15:14.843 --> 01:15:15.877
Aw, come on.

01:15:20.182 --> 01:15:21.516
Wake up.

01:15:21.518 --> 01:15:24.919
Wake up. Come on. Wake up.

01:15:24.921 --> 01:15:28.089
I'm just gonna teach you
a little lesson, right.

01:15:28.091 --> 01:15:29.724
Just a little lesson, okay?

01:15:29.726 --> 01:15:31.292
Okay?

01:15:31.294 --> 01:15:33.494
Don't!

01:15:33.896 --> 01:15:35.763
Don't.

01:15:37.533 --> 01:15:38.900
Don't.

01:16:13.001 --> 01:16:15.169
Hey. Hey, come on.

01:16:15.171 --> 01:16:16.904
Hey. Hey.

01:16:46.835 --> 01:16:49.770
Photographs don't lie.

01:16:49.772 --> 01:16:54.108
In a darkroom,
film comes to life...

01:16:57.145 --> 01:16:59.814
capturing a moment in time.

01:17:01.149 --> 01:17:04.952
Sometimes someone
shows up in your life,

01:17:04.954 --> 01:17:07.922
and you help each other
without even knowing it.

01:17:10.025 --> 01:17:12.226
In here, I feel balanced.

01:17:15.130 --> 01:17:16.697
And out there...

01:17:18.000 --> 01:17:20.167
Hey, can I ask you something?

01:17:20.169 --> 01:17:21.602
Go for it.

01:17:23.372 --> 01:17:25.006
You okay?

01:17:25.008 --> 01:17:26.340
Yeah, I'm cool.

01:17:27.643 --> 01:17:29.210
I'll see you soon?

01:17:29.212 --> 01:17:31.312
Yeah, you'll see me soon.

01:17:37.753 --> 01:17:38.886
You take care.

01:17:38.888 --> 01:17:40.388
You, too.

01:17:40.390 --> 01:17:41.856
And keep taking pictures.

01:17:41.858 --> 01:17:43.824
I will.

